      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 18:51:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国最大谷物港口面临罢工带来的更多中断风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/france-s-biggest-grain-ports-risk-more-disruption-due-to-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国码头工人工会发起了覆盖该国所有港口的一系列罢工，这可能会减缓欧盟最大农业生产国的谷物出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/france-s-biggest-grain-ports-risk-more-disruption-due-to-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 18:20:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗在能源转型中看到 50 万亿美元的商机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/apollo-sees-50-trillion-opportunity-in-energy-transition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私募资本公司阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 合伙人莱斯利·马庞德拉 (Leslie Mapondera) 表示，该公司认为“工业复兴”将成为未来几十年价值 50 万亿美元的能源转型投资机会的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/apollo-sees-50-trillion-opportunity-in-energy-transition</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 17:42:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴尼耶让步，法国勒庞提出预算要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/le-pen-s-party-makes-more-budget-demands-as-barnier-gives-ground</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 做出重要让步放弃提高电力税的计划后，玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 领导的国民联盟进一步要求修改法国政府 2025 年预算法案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/le-pen-s-party-makes-more-budget-demands-as-barnier-gives-ground</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 15:54:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西雷亚尔因支出削减措施令人失望而跌至历史最低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/brazil-s-real-drops-to-all-time-low-as-spending-cuts-fall-flat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西雷亚尔跌至历史最低点，股市出现 2023 年初以来的最大跌幅，因为削减约 120 亿美元公共支出的提议令对该国预算赤字日益担忧的投资者感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/brazil-s-real-drops-to-all-time-low-as-spending-cuts-fall-flat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 12:05:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 关键会议召开前，油价在清淡交投中保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-28</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国感恩节假期交易清淡，油价保持稳定，市场期待即将举行的 OPEC+ 会议，该会议已被推迟至 12 月 5 日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-28</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 23:34:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
