      <title>供应商债务危机导致 Pemex 冻结新承包商交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/pemex-freezes-new-deals-with-contractors-amid-supplier-debt-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥国有石油公司 Petroleos Mexicanos 正在冻结与服务提供商签订的新合同，以偿还欠供应商的约 200 亿美元债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/pemex-freezes-new-deals-with-contractors-amid-supplier-debt-woes</guid>
